# --- keep sensitive / noisy out of Git ---
Security/
**/secrets.json
**/*token*
**/*cookie*
**/*cookies*
.env
.env.*

# Obsidian app-state local only
.obsidian/

# Logs never tracked
99_System_Logs/
00SYSTEM/logs/
**/logs/
*.log

# rclone local config
.rclone_excludes

# (optional) big media; comment out if you truly want them in Git
MEDIA/
